he vertical mortar joint; and</li><li id="_ec048664-1dac-4076-bf6d-85e97e983f41">at not more than 1.2 m centres; and</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_77b03b5b-1457-43bc-99c0-2f46311cb50a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_88b3fb8b-850e-47dd-a104-89974fa98807">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Weepholes are not <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_ed8b2562-4cce-48e6-8e42-77d87f81b93d" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> in the following locations:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_66353450-6491-41b7-81c3-a424ebd17046">Where head openings are less than 1.2 m wide.</li><li id="_606d4231-0baa-4740-82aa-ec138949f582">Beneath <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1525_29.1.0.xml#_48631093-d96b-4a40-a86d-7ffae028f24d" id="_40fee148-5079-412e-a7c9-fab209d2a2d1" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">window</xref> and door sills.</li><li id="_9ae36b41-7cd1-4404-af3f-33d2a49342e1">Where the level of the external impervious surface is elevated for the purpose of providing step-free access <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_d551666d-97b5-45da-9d5c-79f608558366" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/4933#_798b0efb-305e-47b4-9206-3e146fe28df6" id="_3d2a91e3-71de-4f8e-a64b-39643b8cf48d" publishing-id="vol2" referencetype="Text" scope="external" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">H8P1</xref>.</li></ol></subclause></clause>